at a May day parade in Berlin

259
00:31:20,566 --> 00:31:23,035
receiving a salute.

260
00:31:23,167 --> 00:31:25,840
(Smiley) Why would you salute
a cultural attaché?

261
00:31:25,967 --> 00:31:29,517
(Connie) Exactly.
Unless he was a war veteran himself.

262
00:31:29,648 --> 00:31:33,242
And if he was, why hide the fact?

263
00:31:33,367 --> 00:31:34,924
What did you do?

264
00:31:35,046 --> 00:31:37,560
I went straight to Esterhase and Alleline.

265
00:31:38,607 --> 00:31:40,757
Here.

266
00:31:40,887 --> 00:31:44,119
Polyakov is a Karla-trained hood
if ever I saw one.

267
