00:35:42,289 --> 00:35:45,362
(Car pulls up)

313
00:35:45,490 --> 00:35:46,889
(Dog barks)

314
00:36:33,252 --> 00:36:36,085
- Courtesy of Mrs. P.
- Hm?

315
00:36:36,212 --> 00:36:38,202
You been up all night?

316
00:36:39,491 --> 00:36:40,890
Yes.

317
00:36:48,251 --> 00:36:49,571
What's this?

318
00:36:49,692 --> 00:36:54,321
Request for £1,000 in cash
from the Reptile fund.

319
00:36:54,451 --> 00:36:56,601
To a Mr. Ellis.

320
00:36:56,731 --> 00:36:59,166
It was one of Jim Prideaux.
work names.

321
00:37:00,332 --> 00:37:03,005
Prideaux was killed
in Hungary a year ago.

322
00:37:03,132 --> 00:37:04,564
October 21.

323
00:37:05,571 --> 00:37:09,325
So why was someone giving him
£1,000 two months later?

324
00:37:12,132 --> 00:37:14,123
I wonder where he is then, sir.

