I'm getting quite good at ping-pong.

601
01:03:00,075 --> 01:03:01,825
Arabs.

602
01:03:01,953 --> 01:03:04,468
You can rent one but you can't buy one.
Right, Bill?

603
01:03:07,954 --> 01:03:10,549
How's Ricki Tarr these days?

604
01:03:10,675 --> 01:03:13,473
Fine. We have tea
at Fortnum's every afternoon.

605
01:03:15,073 --> 01:03:17,872
