nonsense to get us chasing our tails.

627
01:04:45,275 --> 01:04:46,629
The point is this.

628
01:04:46,756 --> 01:04:48,235
He's heading for home.

629
01:04:49,356 --> 01:04:51,391
The first peep from him,
you come to the grown-ups.

630
01:04:51,515 --> 01:04:53,153
Understood?

