because there was no telegram.

658
01:06:56,676 --> 01:07:00,067
- The whole thing is a fabrication.
- 20th November.

659
01:07:00,197 --> 01:07:03,109
It must have been 20th November.
Evening.

660
01:07:03,237 --> 01:07:05,706
(Tarr on tape) Irina kept telling me
in Moscow Centre...

661
01:07:05,838 --> 01:07:08,227
everybody on the top floor
was laughing themselves sick.

662
01:07:08,358 --> 01:07:11,952
- She told me Karla'...
