663
01:07:12,077 --> 01:07:15,912
Someone is covering their tracks,
unless of course you think

664
01:07:16,038 --> 01:07:17,869
that's just a coincidence?

665
01:07:21,799 --> 01:07:23,312
What about the money?

666
01:07:23,439 --> 01:07:27,192
30,000 isn't so much for Karla
to pay if it protects his mole.

667
01:07:28,717 --> 01:07:32,347
I'm afraid someone in the Circus
knows all about Mr. Tarr

668
01:07:33,718 --> 01:07:36,278
and is doing everything they can
to discredit him.

669
01:07:36,398 --> 01:07:39,707
(Tarr) Everything the Circus thinks
is gold is shit, made in Moscow.

670
01:07:44,078 --> 01:07:47,958
Why didn't you tell me
that you had Tarr?

671
01:07:52,437 --> 01:07:54,508
